"Advanced Animations & Interactions"
Goal: Make the site feel alive and premium

Tasks:
Task 1: Parallax Effects

Add parallax scrolling:
- Hero background elements move slower than foreground
- Section backgrounds with subtle parallax
- Use Framer Motion's useScroll and useTransform hooks
- Create components/effects/ParallaxSection.tsx wrapper

Task 2: Magnetic Hover Effects

Add magnetic buttons/cards:
- Buttons that slightly follow cursor on hover
- Portfolio cards with tilt effect on mouse move
- Use Framer Motion's useMotionValue
- Subtle, not gimmicky (5-10px movement max)

Task 3: Scroll Progress Indicator

Create components/ui/ScrollProgress.tsx:
- Thin bronze line at top showing scroll progress
- Smooth animation
- Fixed position
- Use Framer Motion useScroll


Task 4: Page Transitions

Add smooth page load transitions:
- Fade in content on initial load
- Staggered section reveals
- Loading skeleton for images
- Create components/transitions/PageTransition.tsx

Task 5: Cursor Trail Effect (Optional but cool)
Create custom cursor for desktop:
- Larger cursor with bronze glow
- Follows mouse with slight delay
- Different states for links/buttons
- Only on desktop (hide on mobile)